OL,3,CSNP push for independence would only
OL,4,Cbring joy to despots like Putin `
OL,5,CFindlay
OL,7,FThe Scottish Conservatives have said
OL,8,Fthe SNP's plans for independence would
OL,9,F"only bring joy to despots like Putin".
OL,11,FParty leader Russell Findlay said the
OL,12,F"woke" SNP has turned Holyrood into a
OL,13,Flab for "weird and wacky ideas".
OL,15,FMr Findlay criticised the SNP's gender
OL,16,Fself-ID laws, issues with the CalMac
OL,17,Fferry plans and the continued push for
OL,18,Findependence.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@fO]tD@AOUtD@FO]uD@IOUuD@_O]
