OL,3,CSNP push for independence would only
OL,4,Cbring joy to despots like Putin `
OL,5,CFindlay
OL,7,FHe said: "Woke SNP politicians and
OL,8,Ftheir extremist Green pals have turned
OL,9,FHolyrood into a lab for weird and
OL,10,Fwacky ideas which, unfortunately for
OL,11,Fthe paying public, are not April
OL,12,FFools' Day jokes.
OL,14,F"We've suffered Nicola Sturgeon's
OL,15,Fgender self-ID law that would have
OL,16,Ftrashed women's rights and allowed
OL,17,Fevery male rapist and sex criminal to
OL,18,Fbe legally classed as female.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775012614
OL,3,CSNP push for independence would only
OL,4,Cbring joy to despots like Putin `
OL,5,CFindlay
OL,7,F"Then there's the SNP's stinkingly
OL,8,Fcorrupt CalMac scandal that has seen
OL,9,Fhalf a billion pounds of taxpayers'
OL,10,Fcash spent on two dodgy ferries and
OL,11,FScottish islanders left high and dry.
OL,13,F"And, of course, John Swinney only
OL,14,Fcares about independence, when
OL,15,Fbreaking up the UK would instantly
OL,16,Fmake our great country poorer, less
OL,17,Fstable and less safe and bring joy to
OL,18,Fdespots like Putin.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
