OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775012614
OL,3,CSNP push for independence would only
OL,4,Cbring joy to despots like Putin `
OL,5,CFindlay
OL,7,F"The SNP lanyard class are completely
OL,8,Fdisconnected from what matters to hard-
OL,9,Fworking Scots in the real world and
OL,10,Fthe Scottish Conservatives have been
OL,11,Fthe only party to robustly and
OL,12,Fconsistently stand up to their madness.
OL,14,F"Scots are crying out for some common
OL,15,Fsense from their politicians and the
OL,16,Fbest way to achieve that is to vote
OL,17,FScottish Conservative on your peach
OL,18,Fballot paper on May 7."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@WO]
