OL,3,CSNP push for independence would only
OL,4,Cbring joy to despots like Putin `
OL,5,CFindlay
OL,7,FSNP candidate for Paisley, George
OL,8,FAdam, said: "The biggest April Fool's
OL,9,Fjoke is Russell Findlay continuing to
OL,10,Fspout nonsense that the Tories are in
OL,11,Fcontention in this election.
OL,13,F"Scottish voters won't forgive the
OL,14,FTories for dragging us out of the EU
OL,15,Fagainst our will, crashing the economy
OL,16,Fand leaving us all bearing the cost."
OL,26,@pD@MOUuD@AOUxD@eO]
